Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:08.68,诸神-staff-ja,,0,0,0,,日听：秋水无痕 翻译：yaya 校对：小草爱吃梨 Syura 时间轴：小青
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:07.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう 照れ屋さんなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a shy guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:11.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,っていうか 私なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:24.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここまで来れば もう大丈夫だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're far enough away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:27.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,っつか あの子 強引過ぎだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is way too aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:28.97,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,言わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.16,0:01:31.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.18,0:01:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:32.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誰にも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:34.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,言わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:39.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な 何を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell anyone what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:41.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:42.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,戻ろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemon will get mad at us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:44.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,早くしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:47.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬先輩に怒られる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,if we take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:52.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go back to my room first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:57.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 部屋に戻って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:01.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ そっか じゃあ 先に戻ってっから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Okay, I'll meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure took your sweet time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっと戻ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:09.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わ 悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:11.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一体 二人で何してたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you two up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:13.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そ それは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He was giving me acting tips.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:15.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,演技について教えてもらってたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海ちゃん 完璧主義だから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seaboy is such a little perfectionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:19.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.83,0:02:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it wasn't that big of a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:24.14,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ まあ ちょっとしたことなんだけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:25.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それより 先輩は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, guys! I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:26.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遅くなりました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That took a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:30.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遅かったわね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:31.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何かあったの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:37.12,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あ ええ 別に 何も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:40.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ っつか それよりか イチカ先輩は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's Ichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:42.66,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここにいるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:45.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ いつの間に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:49.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのう 先輩 さっきは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, about what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,撮影 始めましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よい スタート
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And action.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さあ 観念なさい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Give yourself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:01.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,は 話を聞いて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたは犯罪者なのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:06.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,樹下が急に泣き出して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kinoshita started crying all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you want me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you want money, I can pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She showed up out of the blue,{hah, color pun}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:09.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩がいきなり現れて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何も分からないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I just continued filming without making sense of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:13.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カメラ回して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A UFO!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:15.22,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:18.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんか ギクシャクしてるなって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything just felt so awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:18.23,盛夏-JP上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どこどこ どこにいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:24.12,盛夏-JP上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どこ そこ そこにある そこ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,このままじゃいけないんじゃないかって 思ったりまして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It probably can't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:25.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,隙あり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お願い 見逃して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then answer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:32.27,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だったら 私の質問に答えなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:35.97,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたはどうして この星に来たの そして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come to this planet? And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.28,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's your true goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そして 本当の目的を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:45.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海ちゃんが好きなの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like Seaboy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.85,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な 何を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カット
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.34,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ご ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.22,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's film this scene again from a different angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:56.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今のシーン 角度変えてもう一度行きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Tanigawa, help me carry this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.07,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川 バックお願い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Mio, we're moving stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.22,盛夏-JP上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,美桜 移るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Did I surprise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,脅かせちゃいました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:02.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Lemon! Make yourself useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:04.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬先輩も手伝ってくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:05.65,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたはどうなの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm communicating with the movie gods right now. They're descending upon me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:09.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今 まさに 映画の神と交信しているの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:10.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君の
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kaito is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.76,盛夏-JP上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,待って 哲郎さん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait up, Tetsuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:15.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ 千春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アグレッシブだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's pretty aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,有沢さんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What was her name again? Arisawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの子可愛いし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's cute. Tetsuro should just date her already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.51,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎 付き合っちゃえばいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that to Tetsuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:33.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなこと 哲郎君に言っちゃダメだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:35.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:40.32,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,北原さん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,代わりに レフ板持ってくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you hold up the reflective board for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:45.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わ 分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,撮影 続けるわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to continue filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:48.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:49.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Seaboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛く撮ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure I look cute, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:56.42,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イチカ 準備はいい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:58.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん 大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここまで来れば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どこまでですか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:15.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎さん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎は あのまま 戻ってこないし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio went off once we were done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,美桜も 終わった途端 いなくなっちゃうし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Takatsuki vanished too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:25.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,貴月先輩もいないし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.95,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,か 海人君いる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in there, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.29,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼します
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ いない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.32,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,霧島君なら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirishima was in a real hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さっき そそくさと出かけて行ったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:51.95,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,恐らく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume he wants to meet Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:54.66,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,樹下さんのところね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So Kaito really does like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:59.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君 やっぱり 樹下さんのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:00.85,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいえ それはないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんでそう言い切れるんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.27,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,見ていれば分かるもの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell what he's feeling just by looking at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,霧島君の気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just by looking at him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:09.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,見ていれば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then could you tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:15.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの よかったら 教えてもらえませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...tell me how he feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:17.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その 気持ちっていうの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:21.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ええ ゆっくりと語り合いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:29.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,7035室の樹下様は お出かけになっております
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kinoshita from Room 703 is presently away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.22,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.95,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,霧島様でいらっしゃいますよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Mr. Kirishima, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,樹下様から 伝言をお預かりしております
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kinoshita left a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:49.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遅かったですね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You took your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:56.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,待ってください 哲郎さん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Tetsuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer is she gonna chase me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:10.14,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つうか 何時間走らせるんだよ 鉄人か あの子は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she a robot or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:13.17,盛夏-JP上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まってください
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:14.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,美桜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:16.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't be so shy! Come on out, Tetsuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:21.27,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,恥かしがっちゃって 哲郎さん どこですか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また 助けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうな 美桜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be the one thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:33.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お礼だよ 黙っててくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're keeping it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:37.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な なんだっけ それ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:41.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,優しいね 哲郎君は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so nice of you, Tetsuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.41,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I only do that for cute girls, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛い女の子限定だけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや その
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro, you meanie! Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:52.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ひどいじゃないですか 哲郎さん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,にげまわったりして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I don't mind the foreplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういうプレーも嫌いじゃないですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さ デートの続き 楽しみましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's enjoy the rest of our date!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We were on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,い 今まで テートだったの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もちろんです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.07,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ダメ ダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:13.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,呼び出しておいて 遅れてきて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,First you ask me to meet you here, and then you show up late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかも 黙りですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're keeping quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:17.34,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having trouble sorting all this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うまく 考えがまとまらなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:25.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのね ちゃんと 聞いておきたいって思って
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get my thoughts together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you how you really feel... about Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:28.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その 樹下さんは海人君のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:31.29,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その どう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:32.85,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:37.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,って言ったら どうします
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I told you that, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a game to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,か からかってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm just a little jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっと羨ましくて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:45.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,振られちゃったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっと 何するのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bothering Tetsuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:57.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,て 哲郎君が め 迷惑してると思って
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで 迷惑になるわけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:01.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 哲郎さん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell her, Tetsuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや あのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:03.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:04.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,けど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it! You like Tetsuro, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなた 哲郎さんのこと好きなんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:20.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの そ それは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:24.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,可笑しいんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あんたなんて 露出狂のくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just some exhibitionist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.35,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょ おい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私見ちゃったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You had no panties on when you tackled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:32.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたが飛び込んできたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:33.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,下着つけてなかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's weird, right?{\i1} Really{\i0} weird, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.66,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それって可笑しいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:36.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,可笑しいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Admit it!{*}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:37.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとあれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,下着も穿かずに 出歩いて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You go commando and enjoy imagining others finding out! You're just a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:42.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かに見られること想像して楽しんでる変態さんなんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:45.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな女の子に好かれたなんて 哲郎さんは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't like it if a girl like you—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a nudist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:46.65,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,裸族です
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:53.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 ら 裸族なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a nudist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:57.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふ ふら 振られたっていうのは その
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You were dumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君に
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:09:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,By Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.33,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違う 違う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, by a boy at my school in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,東京の学校の先輩に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:09.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,沖縄に来たのは傷心旅行だったりするんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to Okinawa to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだったの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I ran into Seaboy again after so many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:12.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:16.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然 海ちゃんと再会して
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and I tried to act happy to distract myself from how lonely I was feeling after being dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:20.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はしゃいで 彼氏に振られた寂しい気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,紛らわそうとして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I caused some trouble by doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:26.34,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そのことで いっぱい迷惑かけちゃいました
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:30.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:32.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ううん そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:34.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあ そういうことなので
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:37.62,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして あの時泣いていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you crying back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He used the very same words
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.72,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,彼氏に振られた時の言葉をそっくりそのまま
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海ちゃんに言われたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,my boyfriend used to dump me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それ思い出したら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help crying when it all came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,無性に泣けてきちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:58.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの時 海ちゃん こう言ったんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you what Seaboy told me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺には 好きな人がいるって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he has someone he loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと あなたのことだと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he meant you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:08.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell just by looking at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:09.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海ちゃん見てれば 分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I {\i1}have{\i0} known him since we were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これでも 一応幼馴染ですし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you love him too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:16.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それに あなただってそうなんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わ 私は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:22.96,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから お詫びです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.07,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ 樹下っ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ki-Kinoshita!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}See you tomorrow for the movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.41,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,明日も撮影よろしくです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お詫びって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:32.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ 先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:35.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinoshita told me to come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:39.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 樹下に呼ばれて来たんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:41.97,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも どうして 先輩が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.14,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのう 先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:50.63,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かってた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Knew what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:52.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:55.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと 分かってたの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I must've always known.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Spill the beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:01.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そろそろ 教えてくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me how Kaito feels now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:03.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君の気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. If you put this outfit on, I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:04.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この衣装を着てくれれば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,考えないでもないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:11.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ええ またですか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.85,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(863,400)\fs70\blur0.55}Your Feelings{\b1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.85,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(903,181)\blur0.55}Episode Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{part b}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nudist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,裸族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nudist as in you walk around the house naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:17.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えと 裸族って あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:22.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,家の中を全裸でフリーダムで過ごすっていう あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:24.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how my family is, and they raised me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:25.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,家族もそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:28.65,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,幼いごろから 私もそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought everyone did that at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:30.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うちではそうするんだって思ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When I started elementary school, I realized that wasn't true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:35.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,小学校に入ったあたりから なんだか違うなって思い始めたんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell anyone about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんなこと誰にも言えないし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ええっと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're supposed to wear underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:42.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,下着をつけるのが当たり前だってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わかってます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But my blood pressure is really low.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.96,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 私 すごい 低血圧なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes in the morning, I just space out and end up going places without any underwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:50.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,朝ボーっとして たまに 下着を穿き 忘れて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:52.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そのまま 学校行ったりして
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:55.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すごく恥ずかしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's wrong for me to be like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:57.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これじゃ いけないって思って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've tried to break the habit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何度も 何度も 直そうとしたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I still screw up sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.60,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,たまに やっちゃったりして
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be best if no one knew who I was, so I tried to avoid standing out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だったら 目立たないようにしようと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.85,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,影薄くしてたんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but Kanna talked to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:08.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな私に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:12.14,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜が 声かけてきてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and then Tetsuro and Kirishima became my friends too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:16.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎君や 霧島君も 友達になってくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy, and I had so much fun with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:21.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すごく 嬉しくて 楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't want them to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:24.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 知られてたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a pervert...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:28.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 変態なんかじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前 バカじゃねえの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If it happens so often, just keep spares in your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:34.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よく忘れるんなら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:36.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,変えのやつ かばんに入れときゃいいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:38.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そ そう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell people you're going to the bathroom and put them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:40.97,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんで トイレでも行く振りして入ってくりゃいいじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You carry around your PE clothes, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:42.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,体操着だってあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:44.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting all worked up isn't going to solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:46.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,焦ってあたふたしたって物事解決しねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't want anyone to know who you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何が影薄くだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way too cynical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ネガティブ思考すぎるっての
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:54.07,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,困ってんなら 相談しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've told us if you had a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We would've helped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フォローするに決まってんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna and Kai... and me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜も 海も 俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:01.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No buts.{lemme get dat but}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:02.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でもじゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if everyone hated me because of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:06.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆に嫌われたらって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We could never hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:08.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:10.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ホントに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you trust us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺らが信用できねえのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me what's on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:23.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だからさ 言いたいこと言えよ な
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:29.66,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好き
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:35.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎君が 好き
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:38.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大好き
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:42.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,樹下 そんなことあったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what happened with Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she was so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:46.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから あんなに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:49.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんなさいって言ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ 情けない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew she was forcing herself, but I didn't really try to talk to her about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あいつが無理してるの 気づいてたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちゃんと 聞いてやれなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You ended up taking care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩に 任せる形になっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:03.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,樹下さんは海人君に言おうとしてたと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I ended up telling her I wanted to talk first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:08.28,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも その前に 私が呼び出しちゃったから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Kinoshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:09.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,樹下を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:14.07,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,用事でもあったんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:18.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ だから 昼の時 来たんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. So that's why you found us this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something you needed to tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何が言うことでもあったんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.54,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そ それは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:30.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:41.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,綺麗ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They got along so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:07.54,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんかね 二人いい感じで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あたし お邪魔みたいな感じで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like I was just getting in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:13.65,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎さん好きな子いないって言ってたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro said he didn't have someone he liked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I just made a fool of myself!{fuck you anyway}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:16.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私どんだけピエロだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You came with me on this trip so I could escape my heartbreak,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の傷心旅行に付き合ってくれたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and now the same thing happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,同じになっちゃったね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair! She was actually kind of dumb too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:26.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本物の天然 ずるいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:31.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,参っちゃうな この夏 二度目だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the second time this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遅くなっちゃったね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think they're worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:40.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,心配してるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:46.66,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さっきの返事とか いいから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know.{though... yolo}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Ishigaki is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,石垣君 どうしてるかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今も 樹下の連れの子に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably still being chased around by Kinoshita's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:58.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,追い回されてたりして
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess guys can get put off by girls who come on too strong, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:03.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっぱり 女の子にあれだけアプローチされたら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,男の子は悪い気しない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあ それは 多少が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it the same with Kinoshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:09.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,樹下さんの時も
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:12.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いじめないでくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:13.92,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめん ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:19.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:21.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be chased by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 追いかけられるんじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be the one chasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,追いかけていたいんです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to chase after
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きな人のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:31.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,追いかけたい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the girl I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But if my feelings are going to make you uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:36.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.69,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺の気持ちが 先輩を困らせるようなら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:41.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなことない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not uncomfortable at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:45.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,困ってなんか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:46.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:57.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ダっ ダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何してるにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-Ta-Ta-Tanigawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.41,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,たたたた 谷川さん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't doing anything. Wait, why are you wearing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:12.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや これはなんでもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:14.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つうか 何 その 格好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you two until just meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,二人っきりで どこ行ってたんなにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait... Where the hell were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:20.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つうか どこ行ってたんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.54,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょ 何なんです これ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl's night. Just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,二人っきりの女子会をしていたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanigawa, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:28.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川さん 大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Takatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:30.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はあ 貴月先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Tanigawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:34.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な 何してんだよ 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your turn, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:35.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ 海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:38.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:38.95,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何やってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsu-meow and Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎にゃんに 美桜にゃんにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you two, meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:45.34,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,二人でどこ行ってた にゃにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:47.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Where the hell were you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どこ行ってたのにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:50.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.35,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,か 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just leave me here! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずるい ずるい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:54.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私だけ のけもので
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:55.92,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それで 眠い
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't sleep out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ダ ダメだよ こんなとこで寝ちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:01.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何なんだよ これは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:02.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,にゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:14.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You... protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.54,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私をかばって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:18.29,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カット
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Kinoshita has finished all of her scenes, we're done filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:26.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これで 樹下さんのパートは終わり 撮了です
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:28.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お疲れ様
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:29.85,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こちらこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I gotta catch my plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ 私 飛行機の時間あるんで ここで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for keeping you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悪いな ぎりぎりまで粘って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No worries. Good luck with the movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.65,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,平気平気
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:38.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,撮影頑張って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Send me a copy when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,出来上がったら 絶対見せてね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.63,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,樹下さん これ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あ ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Seaboy will be gone if you don't act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:49.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ぼやぼやしてると 海ちゃん 取っちゃいますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:52.54,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna miss her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:02.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,寂しい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:03.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあ 少しは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She was your first love, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,初恋の人ですもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you she wasn't!
