Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,１７時のだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done filming for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:14.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日の撮影は終了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as we clean up the set,
